  <brief_title>Trial of Colistin Versus Meropenem in Ventilator-associated Pneumonia (VAP) (CR-GNB)</brief_title>
  <acronym>MagicBullet</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized, Open Label, Multicenter, Non-inferiority Trial to Compare Safety and Efficacy of Colistin vs. Meropenem in VAP Caused by CR-GNB</official_title>
